'''苯基三氟化硫'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>SF<sub>3</sub>。它可由{{le|二苯基二硫醚|Diphenyl disulfide}}和[[二氟化银|二氟化银]]反应制得。<ref name=William>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=82|issue=17|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=1960-09|pages=4751–4752|doi=10.1021/ja01502a083|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja01502a083|title=ARYLSULFUR TRIFLUORIDES AND PENTAFLUORIDES|accessdate=2021-01-21|author=William A. Sheppard}}</ref>它和[[三氟化硼|三氟化硼]]在无水[[氟化氢|氟化氢]]中反应，可以得到C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>SF<sub>2</sub><sup>+</sup>BF<sub>4</sub><sup>−</sup>。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Fluorine Chemistry|volume=103|issue=1|language=en|date=2000-04|pages=25–29|doi=10.1016/S0022-1139(99)00225-0|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022113999002250|title=Phenyldifluorosulfur(IV)yl salt, C6H5SF2+BF4−|accessdate=2021-01-21|author=A. Jesih|archive-date=2018-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702081755/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022113999002250|dead-url=no}}</ref>它和[[苯甲醛|苯甲醛]]反应，可以得到[[α,α-二氟甲苯|α,α-二氟甲苯]]和[[苯亚磺酰氟|苯亚磺酰氟]]。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Organic Syntheses|volume=44|date=1964|pages=39|doi=10.15227/orgsyn.044.0039|url=http://orgsyn.org/demo.aspx?prep=CV5P0396|title=a,a-DIFLUOROTOLUENE AND BENZENESULFINYL FLUORIDE|accessdate=2021-01-21|archive-date=2018-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180602031546/http://orgsyn.org/demo.aspx?prep=CV5P0396|dead-url=no}}</ref>

